column5: Insane how it just rolls in and smothers them. Does anyone remember this blast ?  http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/news-video/video-two-men-caught-in-sudden-powerful-storm-while-ice-fishing-on-lake-simcoe/article28983593/
That was like a "sno-nado"  True diehards!
That's about what it looked like here but I sure wouldn't have wanted to be out on Simco in it, it was wild enough and I was in the house!
